Version 0.7.3 (2018-08-10)

* Add signal handler to ignore SIGWINCH (fix #8)
* Add GPLv2 license text
* Remove pyfits support in favour of astropy
* Use setuptools instead of distutils

Version 0.7.2 (2016-02-22)

* No-change re-upload to pypi

Version 0.7.1 (2016-02-22)

* Add CPL 7.0.0 to compatibility list
* Minor bugfixes

Version 0.7 (2015-04-01)

* Fully support Python3
* Handle cpl.dfs.ProcessingInfo() for more than one history item
* Better md5sum file path handling for ProcessingInfo
* Connect development with Travis, Coverage, ReadTheManual
* Include test sources in distribution

Version 0.6.2 (2104-03-18)

* Be less strict on CPL compatibility
* Check for cpl-6.4 compatibility

Version 0.6.1 (2013-11-10)

* Fix a crash when a recipe has no parameters

Version 0.6 (2013-11-03)

* Support astropy
* Handle parameter modes (CLI, CFG, ENV)
* Support CPL 6.3.1

Version 0.5 (2013-03-27)

* Support CPL 6.3
* Support Python3

Version 0.4 (2012-11-26)

* Allow to run recipes that are linked to an older CPL
* Allow to overwrite environment variables
* Handle multiline logfiles
* Add a log handling (almost) compatible with the CPL one
* Correctly handle parameters with a dot in the short name

Version 0.3.8 (2012-10-15)

* Better logging in case of crashes
* Better temp file naming
* Bugfixes

Version 0.3.7 (2012-09-14)

* Allow to specify more than one input frame tag
* Allow to specify raw frames as dictionary with tags as key
* Optionally dump of memory after recipe execution
* Remove setuptools usage
* Bugfixes

Version 0.3.6 (2012-03-07)

* Automatically log crashes
* MacOSX compilation fixes
* Bugfixes
